&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and identify target accounts across enterprise hospitals, community hospitals, regional health systems, and medical groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute multi-channel outbound campaigns via email, phone, and LinkedIn to generate qualified meetings for Account Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify inbound leads against Avo&#39;s ideal customer profile and route them to the right AE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a working knowledge of Avo&#39;s products, clinical workflows, and the competitive landscape so your outreach speaks to real buyer pain points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage clinical and operational stakeholders including CMOs, CIOs, IT Directors, and department leaders in initial discovery conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain disciplined activity tracking and pipeline records in HubSpot CRM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with marketing on campaign execution and feedback loops around messaging effectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend industry conferences and events to build relationships and identify new prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hit and exceed monthly and quarterly pipeline generation targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
